"%(inviter_name)s has invited you to join the group \"%(group_name)s\" on "
"%(site_name)s."
msgstr ""
"%(site_name)s இல் உள்ள \"%(group_name)s\" குழுவில் சேர %(inviter_name)s உங்களை "
